{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "N tas KUNGS bij us\nAhbramu fazzijis: Iṣ-\neij no tawas Semmes/\nun no tawas Dsimtenes/ un no\ntawa Tehwa Naimma uhs to\nSemmi/ ko es tew rahdifchu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es darrifchu tew par\nweenu leelu Tantu/ un darrifchu\ntawu Wahrduleelu/ un tu buhfi\nvar Swehtibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es fwehtifchu tohṣ/ kas\ntew fwehti/ un nolahdeschu to/\nkas tew nolahd/ un eekṣch tewis\ntaps wiffas Senimes Ziltis fweh-\ntitas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ahbrams aisgahje/ itt\nka tas KUNGS us to bij tazzi-\njis/ un Lats gahje ar to: Un Ah-\nbrams bija feptindefinits un pee-\nzus Gaddus wezz/ kad wiꞥsch no\nAhrana isgahje.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ahbrams nehme Sa-\nrât fawn Seewu/ un Lattu fawu\nBrahlenu/un wiffu winno Man-\ntu/ ko tee bij fagahdajufchi/ un\ntahs Dwehfeles/ ko tee Ahrana\nbij dabbujuschi/ un tee isgahje/\nka tee eetu us to Semmi Kana-\nan/ un tee nahze us to Semmi\nKanain.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ahbrams pahrstaigaja\nto Semmi/ lihdst tai Weetai Si-\nkiem/ lihdst teeni Oysoleem More/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad rahdtjahs tas KUNGS\nAhbrammam un fazzija: Tawain\nDsimmumain dohſchn es fcho\nSemmi/ un wiꞥsch ustaisija tur\ntam KUNGAM weenu Altari/\nkas winnam bij rahdtjees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥsch zehlahs no tur-\nrenes/ ibs weenain Kalnain Be-\ntelai prett Rihteem/ un uszehle\nfawu Zelti Betelai prett Wakra-\nra-un Ajat prett Austruma puffi/\nun ustaisija tur tam KUNGAM\nweenu Altari/ un peefanze ta\nKUNGA Wahrdn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ahbrams aisgahje ee-\ndams/ un aiseedams prett Dee-\nnas widdus Puffi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tanni Semmê bija\nBads/ un Ahbrams nogahje uhs\nEgipti/ ka wiꞥsch tur weens\nSwechineeks buhtn/ jo tas\nBads bija gruhts tanni Semmê.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas notikkahs/ kad\nwiꞥsch tuwn pee Egiptes nahze/\ntad fazzija wiꞥsch us Sarai fa-\nwu Seewu: Raugi jelle/es sin-\nnu tew skaistu Seewu no Waiga\neffam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad tew tee Egiptexi\nredsehs/ fazzihṣ tee: Schi irr\nwinna Seewa/un nokaus manni/\nun paturrehs tew dsihwn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Sakki jelle/ tew mannu\nMahsu effam/ ka man labbi klah-\njahs tewis deht/in manna Dweh-\nfele tewis labbad dsihwa paleek.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu Ahbrams Egiptes\nSemmê nahze/ tad redseja tee E-\ngipteri\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
